---

<section class="section hiw" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">The process</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color: var(--white);">From first call to live site</h2>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">📞</div>
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">Brief call</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">30 minutes. We learn your business, goals, and deadline — then send a fixed quote the same day. No vague estimates.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-divider" aria-hidden="true">→</div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">⚙️</div>
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">We build</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">Hand-coded, no page builders. You get a staging link within a week and one round of revisions before we finalise.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-divider" aria-hidden="true">→</div>

      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-icon">🚀</div>
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="step-title">You go live</h3>
        <p class="step-desc">We handle hosting, DNS, and launch. Your site is fast, indexed on Google Kenya, and ready to convert visitors from day one.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hiw {
    background: var(--dark);
  }

  .hiw .section-title {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .step {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  .step:first-child {
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .step:last-child {
    padding-right: 0;
  }

  .step-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .step-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .step-divider {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    padding-top: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .steps {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .step {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .step-divider {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
